<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1436,151,378]" pageId="6" pageNumber="68">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,320,231,257]" pageId="6" pageNumber="68">Remarks.</emphasis>
The original description of the genus, especially in the characters of the male genitalia, was rather deficient, the illustrations of the 
<typeStatus box="[610,661,272,298]" pageId="6" pageNumber="68">type</typeStatus>
species not exhibiting these particular configurations of the internal genitalia.
</paragraph>
